PrecisReappointment of BRIAN CHAMBERS, of Charlottetown, Prince Edward Island, as a permanent member of the Veterans Review and Appeal Board, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of one year; and designation of BRIAN CHAMBERS as Chairperson of the Veterans Review and Appeal Board; effective December 19, 2001.
